casebody.data:
Lakshmi ARUNACHALAM, Petitioner,
v.
INTUIT, INC. No. 19-7910. Supreme Court of the United States. May 18, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for *2794writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
